				</p>

				<ol id="ol_li" class="list-group list-group-numbered">
					<li class="list-group-item"><a href="<c:url value='/mypage/cart.do' />">장바구니</a></li>
					<li class="list-group-item"><a href="<c:url value='/mypage/prodqa.do' />">상품문의</a></li>
